name: Lily Greenwood Signed Giclée Print - Butterflies on Red (A4/A3/A2)
description:
Super-high quality Giclée print of 'Butterflies on Red', an original painting by Lily Greenwood. (Mount and frame for illustrative purposes only).

Printed on Somerset Velvet Enhanced 255gsm, an Inkjet paper with the look and feel of a Watercolour paper. This is a beautiful digital art paper, with an immediate finish only seen on authentic art papers.

Produced in the UK using Fine Art Trade Guild approved equipment, inks and paper, Giclée (pronounced 'g-clay') techniques achieve prints of superior archival quality, light-fastness and stability.

The upward swirl of butterflies embodies energy, vitality, positivity, and joy. The butterflies are set to a background of deep crimson red with highlights of gold.

Prints are available in three different sizes, to suit all budgets. 

Small (A4 - 297 x 210mm)      £15.00
Medium (A3 - 420 x 297mm)  £25.00
Large (A2 - 594 x 420mm)     £45.00

These sizes denote the printed area - additional white borders on all sides allow for easier framing, and the addition of a Lily Greenwood initialed signature in the bottom left corner.

These prints are sold unmounted/unframed, to go into a frame of your own style and taste. This also allows easier worldwide shipping, rolled safely into a sturdy postal tube.

Shown photographed in Ikea 'Ribba' frames with custom mounts.

UK delivery (1st Class) £5.00
Each additional item (UK) £1.00

Rest of World delivery (Airmail) £8.00
Each additional item (Rest of World) £2.00
